Package com.sicomsa.dmt

Class SolicitaResponse

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.SatResponse
com.sicomsa.dmt.SolicitaResponse
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SolicitaResponse extends SatResponse
SolicitaResponse is SAT's response from a download request to the massive download web service when requesting a download for the first time of a particular query. The property requestId received can be used to verify the request.
